parameters:
\N<Ruins Thug>Oh, a woman...? Why is there a woman alone in a place like
this...

\N<Ruins Thug>Phew, phew... haah...! D-don't move... if you move, it'll be
worse...!

The man, still in a state of extreme excitement, forcefully
pinned Segi down. His breathing was rough, and he seemed to
be frightened of something.

\N<Ruins Thug>Ah, you're... from Yuia-san's place...! That's right, you're
Segi-san, aren't you...? Why are you in a place like this
doing this...!

\N<Ruins Thug>So, that's it... I get it, right? You were also forced to
join the training corps against your will, weren't you!?

\N<Segi>If that's the case...! If that's the case, what are you
trying to say?! Let go of me... let me go!
\N<Ruins Thug>Haha... I see. You were forced to join too. Just like me.

The man, still excited, put all his strength into the hand
pinning Segi down.

\N<Ruins Thug>...Why are you struggling?! Anyway... we're going to die
anyway! After being made a spectacle by those Luda guys!

\N<Ruins Thug>So, if that's the case...! Then let's at least enjoy the
time we have left while we're alive!
\N<Segi>Don't talk like that...! Please don't give up hope!

\N<Ruins Thug>I will give up... it's inevitable! It's useless, a slow guy
like me has no chance of winning anyway!

\N<Segi>But even so, doing this kind of thing...! What's the point
of hurting each other among townspeople?! Isn't this exactly
what those Luda people want?!

\N<Ruins Thug>I don't know about that...! If we get caught up in a fierce
battle, we'll lose our lives eventually! That won't change!

\N<Ruins Thug>That's right... if we're going to die anyway, I might as
well play into their hands or whatever!

The man, still breathing heavily, reached for Segi's lower
abdomen. His forceful hand trembled slightly as if he was
disturbed.

\N<Ruins Thug>Heh, heh... You women have it good, right?! Using your
bodies to get in good with them and survive everything!
That's right... especially someone like you!

\N<Segi>I would never do such a thing! No matter what happens, I
refuse to kneel before those detestable people!

\N<Ruins Thug>Heh, heh... That's right, then before I give you to them,
I'll have you myself...!

\N<Ruins Thug>What are you doing... How dare you hit my face... And you're
a woman!

\N<Segi>...Whether male or female, everyone in this town is
suffering the same harsh reality. But giving in to your
desires and running wild is exactly what they want.
\N<Segi>If we do that... nothing will be resolved.

\N<Segi>I've kept quiet about this... to the people around us. So
please, don't give up on yourself, and keep moving forward
with determination.
\N<Ruins Thug>Shut up! Damn it! Don't preach to me! Damn it!!

\N<Segi>(No, this won't do... This person is terribly frightened...
If I provoke him further...)
\N<Segi>(But I can't let this go on... any further...)

\N<Ruins Thug>Heh, heh... What's wrong, Miss Segi!? What are you thinking
about...!?

The man reached for Segi's clothes and put more force into
his hand as it moved towards her lower abdomen. Contrary to
the excited state of the man, Segi's body momentarily lost
its strength.

\N<Ruins Thug>Heh, heh...! What's the matter, suddenly becoming so
docile...!?

\N<Ruins Thug>Oh, is that it...? Have you finally understood what I'm
saying...?

\N<Ruins Thug>That must be it, right...? That's what it is, isn't it?
Because I've heard rumors that you're a kind woman...!

\N<Ruins Thug>So, if that's the case... It's okay, right...? You're going
to comfort me... right...!?

\N<Ruins Thug>What are you doing... How dare you hit my face... And you're
a woman!

\N<Segi>...Whether male or female, everyone in this town is
suffering the same harsh reality. But giving in to your
desires and running wild is exactly what they want.
\N<Segi>If we do that... nothing will be resolved.

\N<Segi>I've kept quiet about this... to the people around us. So
please, don't give up on yourself, and keep moving forward
with determination.
\N<Ruins Thug>Shut up! Damn it! Don't preach to me! Damn it!!
